{"id": 3115, "genre": 1001, "title": "本职工作以外，你还做过哪些“伪工作”？", "description": "感觉自己就是一个“工具人”。（题图来自：iStock ©️Aleksei Morozov ）", "record_count": 1391, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20200106191830ExijLe5cVJN2Xvgm.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-06T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 352016, "content": "统计各种各样的数据，而有些根本和我的本职没有关联。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677032}, {"id": 352550, "content": "秘书下班酒店休闲系列？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051188}, {"id": 351785, "content": "加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506438}, {"id": 351534, "content": "帮领导洗茶壶、察言观色掌握倒茶水的时机", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351535, "content": "被安排动手组装办公室桌椅/搭建会场…美其名曰锻炼能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351536, "content": "写完全没人看的公文／做周报…", "image": null, "praise_count": 151, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351537, "content": "因为从事技术工作，谁的电脑出问题了就来找我修电脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351552, "content": "太多了，创业公司基本上是哪个职位缺人随便抓个会的补上，有的甚至不聘请保洁阿姨，让员工天天做值日。有的不聘请宣发，让员工天天发朋友圈，美名其曰团结就是力量，分明是资本就是压榨劳动力。工作没多久，已经学会藏技能和推开甩来的锅。", "image": null, "praise_count": 141, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 351553, "content": "本职教学\n\n打扫卫生，修过塑机，投影仪各种修，保姆，化妆师，组织剧场，心理医生，哎想想好心累，天天累的和狗一般。工资却少的可怜", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676572}, {"id": 351554, "content": "虽然我会excel，但是老师您也不能天天叫我去帮忙处理啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627500}, {"id": 351555, "content": "团 建", "image": null, "praise_count": 361, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 351557, "content": "兼招聘，产品线上运营，采购，制作各种雨我无瓜的表格", "image": "img/option/option/202001070941033zNIpHWey9tBASwM", "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664029}, {"id": 351558, "content": "加班的时候明明没有工作活都做完了，还装作很认真的样子…", "image": null, "praise_count": 115, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354880}, {"id": 351559, "content": "被自愿转发朋友圈🙂", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282904}, {"id": 351562, "content": "做咖啡师期间，要学会把冷柜里已经过期的食品，悄悄的改好时间条。别赞要脸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194233}, {"id": 351563, "content": "年会", "image": "img/option/option/20200107120347TXDLlmwvcyK3SJqx.jpg", "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1671014}, {"id": 351564, "content": "背锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054974}, {"id": 351565, "content": "每日想起来就写的所谓工作总结", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1663808}, {"id": 351566, "content": "年终总结ppt和来年规划", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852421}, {"id": 351570, "content": "热爱工作", "image": "img/option/option/20200107160819gF7Rnb85LKPwE0dp.png", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471874}, {"id": 351572, "content": "我一个室内设计狗，兼职报价销售监工修电脑修打印机，这我还能勉强理解；可为什么老板儿子的ppt也要我来做...", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517754}, {"id": 351577, "content": "日报周报", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 297886}, {"id": 351583, "content": "每年都被拉去年会上跳舞💃🏻我分明是个身材不美观的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251362}, {"id": 351584, "content": "取钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676648}, {"id": 351586, "content": "刷油漆", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026880}, {"id": 351587, "content": "兼出纳很闲的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676655}, {"id": 351589, "content": "我好端端一个做新闻的，缺额外做了人资。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373892}, {"id": 351590, "content": "帮老板买咖啡，帮老板印资料，帮老板订餐厅", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457910}, {"id": 351592, "content": "做青年大学习不知道算不算哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291669}, {"id": 352617, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186578}, {"id": 351594, "content": "帮老板搬家、收家", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572473}, {"id": 351596, "content": "被裹挟加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675230}, {"id": 351597, "content": "转发推送，会议充人头", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676218}, {"id": 351598, "content": "宣传稿\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215971}, {"id": 352366, "content": "宣传部负责策划活动安排一切事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627030}, {"id": 351600, "content": "哪有正经工作？", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538231}, {"id": 351610, "content": "没有主要负责的工作岗位，但是动脑子的日程却从一个会议室到另一个会议室从未停止过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676744}, {"id": 351614, "content": "莫名其妙的架构改革，发展方案，作战计划，人工智能，科技负能", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156397}, {"id": 351615, "content": "帮老师搬家，带孩子，我们是学生干部，不是学生奴才。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299011}, {"id": 351651, "content": "年会", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666377}, {"id": 352427, "content": "工作做完了还不能走", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1684369}, {"id": 351661, "content": "这工作我在与不在不会产生区别。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658445}, {"id": 352430, "content": "在群里发大拇指", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991013}, {"id": 352439, "content": "给领导写发言稿/申请课题/写论文······", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924904}, {"id": 352203, "content": "进一个错的公司，团队，小组.......感觉都tmd不该我做", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627183}, {"id": 351712, "content": "团建&年会&背锅 🙃", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657367}, {"id": 351725, "content": "合影留念", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338462}]}